### Create a new ticket
POST http://localhost:5089/tickets
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Sample Ticket",
  "description": "This is a test ticket",
  "status": "Open"
}

### Update ticket status
PUT http://localhost:5089/tickets/2/status
Content-Type: application/json

"InProgress"

### Get ticket by ID
GET http://localhost:5089/tickets/2
Accept: application/json

### Get all tickets (no filter)
GET http://localhost:5089/tickets

### Get all tickets filtered by status Open
GET http://localhost:5089/tickets?status=Open